		},
		{
			"id": 3,
			"parent": 0,
			"text": "We will refer to a negation word as the negator and the text span within the scope of the negator as the argument . <S>\r",
			"relation": "ROOT"
		},
		{
			"id": 4,
			"parent": 3,
			"text": "Commonly used heuristics \r",
